where id = object_id('ItemMstrDetail')
and type = 'U')
drop table ItemMstrDetail

/* Table: ItemMstrDetail */
/*==============================================================*/
create table ItemMstrDetail (
ID int null,
Item_Code varchar(20) null,
MouldCode varchar(20) null,
ModeDesc varchar(200) null,
MaterialCode varchar(20) null,
MaterialDesc varchar(20) null,
CreateDate datetime null
)
go
